author: jocaba
msg: Added MSBuildPlugin for support on WPF/WCF projects with XAML files. The MSBuildPlugin will generate the needed files for building these projects. Also modified the importer to auto append the plugin if the project contains those XAML files.
Added the documentation in Importing Projects part of the docs.

author: jocaba
msg: added checking for versioning of the dependency to get first if available in the sequence of solution,project, 1.0-SNAPSHOT

author: brett
msg: workaround bug in plugin plugin > 2.4.1 and < 2.5.1 which are used by recent versions of Maven by default. Use the latest plugin tools and temporarily upgrade qdox until a new release is available
